  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then came June 22, and suddenly the talk that there was war with Germany, that Germany attacked Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The days just before that, the trains were going west from Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That must have been part of the agreement that they had, where they used to supply the raw material to Hitler, and-- and there was-- we were living right next to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you could resolve to stop those heavy trains moving west, west, day and night, day and night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was-- oh, I was elated when the war was on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I figured, OK, now, it's going to be Russia too in the war, and really the Germany is going to get it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I thought it's-- it's-- it's time that now the-- the French and German, England is having an ally, and Germany is going to get it from both sides.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was absolutely happy as can be at the time, I remember it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you that during the time, I was already exposed to the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to run to stay in line to get the major paper.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was way ahead of boy of 11, 12 years old, as far as knowledge, what goes on in the world, the wars, the positions of the armies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "North Africa, I knew it like-- like my hand, as to whether it was Benghazi, Derna, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Trobruk, and then back and forth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was acquainted with that stuff.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I knew it like ad",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "25th.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First impression was  we-- we had-- we build a-- a big hole at the-- kind of digged into the-- a big hole in the ground away from our house.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
